---
title: Beyond Meat® and Black Bean Chili with Cheddar Cheese and Sour Cream
description: Nothing says autumn like a big bowl of warm chili! In this oh -so-quick and tasty version, Beyond Meat® is stewed with black beans. It wouldn't be chili without the fixins', so we're topping it off with sour cream, cheddar cheese and spiced tortilla chips!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chili-au-beyond-meat-et-aux-haricots-noirs-85fbc95c.jpg
